snippet.title: Deep Space Survivor - Trailer - 1.0
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2066730/Deep_Space_Survivor/

Deep Space Survivors is out now on Itch.io! https://risse.itch.io/deep-space-survivor

In the game you try to survive the various enemy space ships in bullet hell style, blowing them up with different weapons and powerups. Influenced by Vampire Survivors and Magic Survival, this game provides tons of action and progression.

Song: iFeature - Rush [Arcade Release] Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds Free Download/Stream: http://ncs.io/rush
